result:
<!-- 新增弹框 -->
<a-modal
  title="新建"
  style="top: 20px;"
  :width="600"
  v-model="visible"
  @ok="handleSubmit"
  v-preventReClick
  destroyOnClose="true"
  :maskClosable="false"
>
  <a-form :form="form">
    <a-form-item label="版本描述" :labelCol="labelCol" :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
      <a-textarea
        placeholder="请输入描述"
        :rows="4"
        v-decorator="[
          'contents',
          {rules: [{ message: '请输入描述' }]}
        ]"
      />
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item label="上传" :labelCol="labelCol" :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
      <a-upload
        name="file"
        :multiple="false"
        :action="url"
        :fileList="fileList"
        :headers="headers"
        @change="handleChange"
      >
        <a-button>
          <a-icon type="upload" />点击上传
        </a-button>
      </a-upload>
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
</a-modal>
